about.summary: Fast matrix-multiplication as a self-contained Python library – no system dependencies!

name: cython-blis
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "cython-blis" %}
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}
{% set sha256sum = "d5dfb6adc2ec93b8f32006f8eb1f85e569ace0ef998b4e7bb6d9676ebe0010ce" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/b/blis/blis-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256sum }}

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win and py27]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - clangdev  # [win]
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
    - numpy 1.15.*
    - wheel >=0.32,<0.33
  run:
    - python
    - numpy >=1.15.0

test:
  imports:
    - blis
    - blis.py
    - blis.cy

about:
  home: http://github.com/explosion/cython-blis
  license: BSD
  license_family: BSD
  license_file:
    - LICENSE
    - blis/LICENSE
  summary: 'Fast matrix-multiplication as a self-contained Python library – no system dependencies!'

  doc_url: https://github.com/explosion/cython-blis
  dev_url: https://github.com/explosion/cython-blis

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - honnibal
    - ines
